  <summary date="2021-01-27T17:35:41Z" status="Introduced in House">Go to High School, Go to College Act of 2019

This bill requires the Department of Education to carry out a pilot program that awards College in High School Federal Pell Grants to high school students for enrollment in and completion of postsecondary courses offered through dual or concurrent enrollment programs or early college high schools.</summary>
